READ
  Read incoming telegrams.

SYNTAX
  read
  rea

DESCRIPTION
  Reads all unread telegrams addressed to your country, in the order
  they were received.  Each telegram shows the sender, timestamp,
  and message body.

  After you read all telegrams, the unread count resets to zero.
  Telegrams are not deleted after reading — they can be reviewed
  again in the next session.

  Your unread telegram count is shown when you log in.

EXAMPLE
  read                      read all unread telegrams

SEE ALSO
  telegram  announce  relations
